ly heated. Nike clarified that this combination is intended to \\\"drive heat deep into the muscle and tissue in the foot and ankle, helping athletes move, perform and recover naturally much faster.\\\" The battery cell, which is situated in the insole of each shoe, regulates the three levels of compression and heat that the boots provide. Athletes can choose to control the heat and compression of both shoes simultaneously with a single button or adjust each shoe individually.\\nThe collaborative vest utilizes thermoelectric coolers to deliver immediate heating and cooling capabilities without requiring ice or liquid. According to Nike, this feature enables athletes to \\\"dial their body temperatures to their exact specifications during warm-ups and cool-downs.\\\" Hyperice, a company renowned for its innovative recuperation technology, contributes its expertise to this partnership, supplementing Nike's product line with state-of-the-art thermal and compression technology. This collaboration represents a substantial advancement in the development of recovery solutions and optimal athletic performance.\\nBecome a Subscriber\\nPlease purchase a subscription to continue reading this article.\\nSubscribe Now\\n\\nRead more\\n\\n\\n\\n\\njirehl  \\n \\nRELATED ARTICLESMORE FROM AUTHOR\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n Software & Data \\n\\nNVIDIA Launches Comprehensive Suite of Healthcare Microservices to Advance AI-Driven Medical Innovations \\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n Biotech \\n\\nAurion Biotech Gains FDA Fast-Track Designations for Corneal Therapy \\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n Consumer Internet \\n\\nDirect-to-Consumer Medical Tests Gain Traction \\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n Companies \\n\\nPfizer Struggles with Employee Morale Amid Business Turnaround \\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n Medical Devices \\n\\nMedical Device Makers Prepare to Phase Out PFAS \\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n Companies \\n\\nDuPont to Acquire Donatelle Plastics, Enhancing Healthcare Capabilities \\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n Features \\n\\nAI\\u2019s Role in Addre