l get special access to premium content and trend research that cannot be found anywhere else.\\nView last week's newsletter\\n\\n\\nSUBSCRIBE NOW\\n\\nFollow Trend Hunter\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nAllAITechLifeCultureDesignAdsBusinessEcoGoodLuxuryFashionBizarreKeynotes\\nDASHBOARD\\nRESEARCH\\nKEYNOTES\\nEVENTS\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nUltra-Wide Head-Mounted Displays\\n\\n\\n\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPreviousSet ofRelatedIdeas\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tarrow_back\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nRevolutionary Long-Throw Projectors\\n\\n\\n\\nProductivity-Focused Smart Glasses\\n\\n\\n\\nAI-Connected Sports Glasses\\n\\n\\n\\nThree-Dimensional Mixed-Reality Displays\\n\\n\\n\\nFeatherlight Entertainment Eyewear\\n\\n\\n\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tNextSet ofRelatedIdeas\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tarrow_forward\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n33 SIMILARPHOTOS\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nThe GOOVIS ART Head-Mounted Display is ImmersiveMichael Hemsworth \\u2014 July 13, 2024 \\u2014 Tech References: indiegogo & gadgetify\\nShare on Facebook\\nShare on Twitter\\nShare on LinkedIn\\nShare on Pinterest\\nThe GOOVIS ART ultra-wide head-mounted display is the brand's latest wearable engineered with a next-generation experience in mind. The headset works by being positioned onto the head and shifting the viewer into position over the eyes where it will go to work creating the visual experience of a 110-inch display at a four-meter distance. The headset weighs in at 110-grams and can be folded down when not in use to work well for users transitioning between various locations.\\n\\nThe GOOVIS ART ultra-wide head-mounted display works in a variety of modes including multitasking, focus and relaxed, while also offering compatibility with most smartphones, drones, gaming consoles and more. The headset offers compatibility with both 2D and 3D content, while the ultra-wide peripheral view will maximize viewing comfort.\\nTrend Themes\\n\\n1. Wearable Ultra-wide Displays - The rise of ultra-wide head-mounted displays offers a new level of immersive experiences for users across various applications.\\n\\n2. Multifunctional Headsets - Headsets that provide multitasking and focus modes are redefining user interaction by enhancing productivity and relaxation.\\n\\n3. Foldable Wearable Technology - Foldable wearable devices are becoming increasingly popular due to their portability and convenience for users on the go.\\n\\n\\nIndustry Implications\\n\\n1. Consumer Electronics - Innovations in head-mounted displays are pushing forward the boundaries of how consumers engage with multimedia and gaming.\\n\\n2. Drone Technology - The integration of head-mounted displays with drones is transforming how users perceive and interact with aerial footage.\\n\\n3. Smartphone Accessories - Advancements in headset compatibility with smartphones are unlocking new potentials for augmented and virtual reality experiences.\\n\\n6.2ScorePopularityActivityFreshnessVIEW MORE STATS expand_moreGET A CUSTOM REPORTSUBSCRIBE TO ADVISORY\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\t\\t\\t\\tLearn to Hunt Ideas\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nImmersive VR Headset Displays\\nThe LG 4K OLEDoS Display Measures in at 1.3-Inches in Size\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nplay_circle_filled\\n\\nHead-Mounted HD Displays\\nThe GOOVIS G3X Accepts Video Inputs up to 4k Resolution\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nplay_circle_filled\\n\\nPortable Holographic Displays\\nLooking Glass Go Shares Memories as 3D Holograms, Not Photos\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nDigital Professional VR Headsets\\nThis Office VR Headset Concept by Simon Ljungblahd is Intuitive\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nTop 100 Tech Trends in June\\nFrom AI Job Skill Tools to Auto-Adaptive 3D Printers\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nTop 100 Tech Trends in February\\nFrom Professional Quad-Lens Smartphones to AI-Powered Cat Doors\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nTop 100 Mobile Trends in June\\nFrom Iconic Artist Phone Cases to Complimentary Health Apps\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nTop